WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Every morning when I wake up, through the window I can see the Matterhorn.

2
00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:07.000
It's a beautiful day.

3
00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:14.000
At Erzermatt, it's like a big family for all of us.

4
00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:16.500
[ church bells ]

5
00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:22.500
[ siren ]

6
00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:25.500
[ helicopter ]

7
00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:28.000
We do around 1,700 rescues a year.

8
00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:29.000
You have to stay focused.

9
00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:32.000
You never know how close you are to the limit.

10
00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Every mistake you do could be your last.

11
00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:37.500
[ helicopter ]
